headline: Target and Ulta Beauty to end shop-in-shop partnership
summary: The retail concept will continue in stores and on Target.com until August 2026.

headline: Target and Ulta’s ‘conscious uncoupling’
summary: A shop-in-shop deal ends as both companies turn attention back to retail basics. Analysts weigh in on the move while Bank of America downgraded Target.
